to show task manager on terminal 
$ top

to reboot the linux system
$ sudo reboot

remove program from fedora
$ sudo yum remove pitivi
if program consist many packages and need remove with all packages
$ sudo yum remove wine*
to get list related packages on some application. This help to see if any package did't remove with application.
rpm -qa | grep wine

to update fedora applications
$ sudo dnf update
